WEBVTT

00:11:57.197 --> 00:12:01.563
Usposobljeni prostovoljci
bi morali sedeti v čakalnicah,

00:12:01.563 --> 00:12:03.530
biti na telefonu,

00:12:03.530 --> 00:12:05.930
v spletnih forumih,

00:12:05.963 --> 00:12:08.063
na voljo za pogovor.

00:12:08.063 --> 00:12:11.297
Mlade v šoli

00:12:11.330 --> 00:12:13.730
učimo o imunskem sistemu

00:12:13.763 --> 00:12:15.463
in o tem, kako

00:12:15.497 --> 00:12:17.963
so cepiva, ki so jih dobili
njihovi mlajši bratje,

00:12:17.997 --> 00:12:23.363
okrepila njihov naravni
imunski sistem.

00:12:23.363 --> 00:12:25.930
Zato je to dobra stvar.

00:12:27.330 --> 00:12:29.130
Zgraditi moramo to zaupanje,

00:12:29.163 --> 00:12:30.630
poslušati moramo.